## Remarks

<span data-ttu-id="de2aa-102">运行状况终结点用于执行评估的一个组件的运行状况的运行状况检查。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de2aa-102">Health endpoints are used to perform health checks that assess the health of a component.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="de2aa-103">运行状况终结点可以用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de2aa-103">Health endpoints can be used to:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="de2aa-104">通知的业务流程工具来终止进程，正在故障严重运行状况检查。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de2aa-104">Notify orchestration tools to kill a process that is failing a critical health check.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="de2aa-105">充当通过跟踪和提供有关可用性和服务的性能警报来监视工具的早期问题指示器。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de2aa-105">Serve as an early problem indicator for monitoring tools by tracking and providing alerts about the availability and performance of a service.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="de2aa-106">`ServiceHealthBehavior` 是一个 WCF 服务行为，扩大了 IServiceBehavior 也派生自<xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceHealthBehaviorBase>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de2aa-106">`ServiceHealthBehavior` is a WCF service behavior that extends IServiceBehavior and derives from <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceHealthBehaviorBase>.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="de2aa-107">添加`ServiceHealthBehavior`实例向<xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceDescription.Behaviors?displayProperty=nameWithType>集合启用下列：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de2aa-107">Adding a `ServiceHealthBehavior` instance to the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceDescription.Behaviors?displayProperty=nameWithType> collection enables the following:</span></span>

-   <span data-ttu-id="de2aa-108">**发布服务的运行状况：** 特定于服务的详细信息，如服务状态，限制计数，并且可以使用 HTTP/GET 请求与显示容量`?health`查询字符串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de2aa-108">**Publication of Service Health:** Service-specific details such as service state, throttle counts, and capacity can be displayed using an HTTP/GET request with the `?health` query string.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="de2aa-109">了解并轻松地使其可以访问到显示的信息是至关重要的表现不正常的 WCF 服务进行故障排除时。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de2aa-109">Knowing and easily having access to the information displayed is of paramount importance when troubleshooting a misbehaving WCF service.</span></span>

-   <span data-ttu-id="de2aa-110">**返回的 HTTP 响应代码：** 一个可以在查询字符串中指定的 HTTP/GET 运行状况探测请求的 HTTP 状态代码。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de2aa-110">**Return of HTTP response codes:** One can specify in the query string the HTTP status code for an HTTP/GET health probe request.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="de2aa-111">运行状况终结点才有意义，它将监视其运行状况的组件的上下文中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de2aa-111">A health endpoint is only meaningful in the context of the component whose health it monitors.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="de2aa-112">它具有其他含义或用途。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de2aa-112">It has no other meaning or purpose.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="de2aa-113">在这种情况下，其运行状况是交互的媒介的组件的运行状况。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de2aa-113">As such, its health is a conduit to the health of the component.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="de2aa-114">客户端*应*假设适用于整个组件运行状况终结点返回的 HTTP 响应代码。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de2aa-114">Clients *should* assume that the HTTP response code returned by the health endpoint is applicable to the entire component.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="de2aa-115">这是与当前基础结构的工具，利用运行状况检查，如负载均衡器、 服务发现和其他所需的行为兼容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de2aa-115">This is compatible with the behavior expected by current infrastructural tooling that utilize health checks, such as load-balancers, service discoveries, and others.</span></span>

### <a name="enable-a-health-endpoint"></a><span data-ttu-id="de2aa-116">启用运行状况终结点</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de2aa-116">Enable a health endpoint</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="de2aa-117">有两种方法来指定如何公开运行状况终结点和发布 WCF 服务运行状况信息：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de2aa-117">There are two ways to specify how to expose the health endpoint and publish WCF service health information:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="de2aa-118">通过使用配置文件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de2aa-118">By using a configuration file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="de2aa-119">例如:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de2aa-119">For example:</span></span>

   ```xml
   <behaviors>
     <serviceBehaviors>
       <behavior name="DefaultBehavior">
         <serviceHealth httpGetEnabled="true"/>
       </behavior>
     </serviceBehaviors>
   </behaviors>
   ```

- <span data-ttu-id="de2aa-120">以编程方式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de2aa-120">Programmatically.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="de2aa-121">下面的代码片段使用C#公开运行状况终结点：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="de2aa-121">The following code fragment uses C# to expose the health endpoint:</span></span>

    ```csharp
    ServiceHost host = new ServiceHost(typeof(Service1),
        new Uri("http://jconde-dev1:81/Service1"));
    ServiceHealthBehavior healthBehavior =
                host.Description.Behaviors.Find<ServiceHealthBehavior>();
    if (healthBehavior == null)
    {
        healthBehavior = new ServiceHealthBehavior();
    }
    //healthBehavior.HttpGetEnabled = false;
    //healthBehavior.HttpsGetEnabled = false;
    host.Description.Behaviors.Add(healthBehavior);
    ```
